###> symfony/asset-mapper ###
/public/assets/
# Ignore everything under assets/vendor (re-downloaded by `bin/console importmap:install`)…
/assets/vendor/*
# …EXCEPT crossvent, which must be committed. jsDelivr re-bundled crossvent@1.5.5's +esm
# with a newer Rollup whose namespace import Symfony's resolver fails to rewrite, so a
# fresh `importmap:install` produces a relative `import ... from "./npm/custom-event@1.0.1/+esm"`
# that 404s at runtime and breaks ALL page JS. The committed copy keeps the correct bare
# `import ... from "custom-event"`; importmap:install never overwrites existing files.
!/assets/vendor/crossvent/
###< symfony/asset-mapper ###

